        <h2 style="font-size:2rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--gray-900);margin-bottom:1.25rem;letter-spacing:-0.02em;line-height:1.3">Free Online Resume Builder — Create Professional Resumes in Minutes</h2>
        <p style="font-size:1.0625rem;color:var(--gray-500);margin-bottom:2rem;line-height:1.7">Looking for a free resume builder that creates professional, ATS-friendly resumes without any hassle? You've found it. Our online resume builder lets you create a polished, job-winning resume in minutes — completely free, with no sign-up required. Whether you're a seasoned executive, a recent graduate, or switching careers, our tool gives you everything you need to land your next interview.</p>

