            <h3 style="font-size:0.9375rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--gray-900);margin-bottom:0.375rem">ATS-Friendly Templates</h3>
            <p style="font-size:0.8125rem;color:var(--gray-500);line-height:1.5">All templates are designed to pass Applicant Tracking Systems with clean layouts and proper semantic structure.</p>
