        <h3 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray-900);margin:2.5rem 0 1rem;letter-spacing:-0.01em">How to Use This Resume Builder</h3>
        <p>Using our resume generator is simple. Start by filling in your personal information and professional summary. Add your work experience with bullet points highlighting key achievements. Include your education details, skills organized by category, notable projects, certifications, and languages. You can arrange sections in any order, toggle visibility, and see changes instantly in the live preview. When you're satisfied, export your resume as a PDF with one click.</p>

        <h3 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray-900);margin:2.5rem 0 1rem;letter-spacing:-0.01em">Tips for Creating an Effective Resume</h3>
        <p>When using our resume builder online, follow these tips for best results: Tailor your resume to each job application by adjusting keywords from the job description. Use action verbs and quantify achievements (e.g., "Increased sales by 30%"). Keep your resume to one page if you have less than 10 years of experience. Use a professional email address. Proofread carefully — a single typo can cost you an interview. Our resume CV builder helps you create a document that hiring managers will notice for all the right reasons.</p>

        <p style="margin-top:2rem">Check your resume's <a href="/ats-score" style="color:var(--primary);text-decoration:none;font-weight:500">ATS compatibility score</a>, generate a matching <a href="/cover-letter" style="color:var(--primary);text-decoration:none;font-weight:500">cover letter</a>, or browse <a href="/resume-examples" style="color:var(--primary);text-decoration:none;font-weight:500">resume examples by industry</a>.</p>
